title: Auld Lang Syne
description:
Our story tonight is called Auld Lang Syne, and it’s a story about daybreak on a new year. It’s also about a little book with a page missing, what we let go of and what we keep and the scent of woodsmoke on a January morning.
Buy the book:http://hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens
